title: Your download page doesnt open
body: Hey all. Decided to re download the game after running into the launcher not opening. Once I clicked on the link it sent me to a blank white page. Riot: not sure if you guys are aware of this. Also im not sure if this is just a problem on my end, anyone having any luck?

replies.body:
Hey Frizzko! 

We were performing maintenance on the Download page. This should be resolved now! Feel free to reply to this if you have any questions!

Cannot open the download page either, i get a blank white page. Reset Safari and tried to refresh reopen league site multiple times...not sure what to do? all other links open on site but to the download page.
